{"tid":1485881,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人！撳錢！！","createTime":"2019-08-18T17:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T18:28:40.000Z","uid":58257,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6950922bd3194769e979f235cb92db4843996e2f","tid":1485881,"uid":58257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:00:50.000Z","msg":"如果唔中意嗌加油，可以試下嗌撳錢。<br />\n可以一齊嗌之餘，又有文宣既作用。<br />\n大家繼續一齊撳撳撳，撳撚曬d錢出黎！！！"},{"pid":"3b4c2c073cc07622e94e8fe1558e2a7355425a52","tid":1485881,"uid":295738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:01:45.000Z","msg":"唔好再分化，捉鬼，割蓆！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485784\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485784</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n嗌五大訴求最重要"},{"pid":"b60aa144942384f963d0397a3bfe9364b33cbebe","tid":1485881,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:03:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7bb9069f642896bcaa1496f7cb4b4cb143cedaa2","tid":1485881,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:06:29.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n加油間唔中嗌幾下就算喇<br />\n真係嗌番啲訴求/ 行動 (eg. 818維園見/ 撳錢) 會好好多"},{"pid":"9e538f5dcdebd33b0d42c565bdfe71ab4c5fa20e","tid":1485881,"uid":58257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:19:15.000Z","msg":"因為現場見，嗌某d口既時候會比較冷淡<br />\n而嗌香港人加油既時候係最熱心同齊心<br />\n不過我覺得嗌加油又好似冇咩意思，所以諗可唔可以嗌「撳錢」黎代替。"},{"pid":"a380da10e59262f84c2338552b0e75f28a488f31","tid":1485881,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:27:06.000Z","msg":"我今日有試嗌香港人撳錢，附近有人會笑再一齊嗌<br />\n但始終好多人都係嗌加油，好快就蓋過左<br />\n但算係個好開始，keep住同幾個人嗌 好快就識"},{"pid":"93301de0f603c5f374ca92ce98b6d4d3f5bc8310","tid":1485881,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:28:40.000Z","msg":"差d唔記得咗"}]}